title: The Von Haessler Doctrine Special Edition S7/E033 - Pope Trump
description: In a collaborative effort, The Von Haessler Doctrine and Mark Arum Show mixed it up with both shows filling-in for The Von Haessler Doctrine. Join Mark, Tim, Jared, Autumn, and Debra as they chat about confessions, fast food, the post-Trump presidency, and much more!
